MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 846

DECLARING AS CIVIL RESERVATION FOR SUB-CAPITOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE PROVINCE OF CAGAYAN, A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED AT BARANGAY BANGAG, MUNICIPALITY OF LALLO, PROVINCE OF CAGAYAN, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby declare as civil reservation for sub-capitol site purposes of the Province of Cagayan, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated at Barangay Bangag, Municipality of Lallo, Province of Cagayan, Island of Luzon, containing an area of Two Hundred Thirty Four Thousand Eight Hundred Eleven (234,811) square meters , more or less, subject to private rights, if any there be, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

SWO-(AF)-02-000028

A PARCEL OF LAND, Plan SWO-(AF)-02-000028, situated at Barangay Bangag, Municipality of Lallo, Province of Cagayan, Island of Luzon.

Bounded on the E., & NW., along lines 1-2-3, both by Bangag Elementary School; on the NE., along line 3-4 by National Highway; on the E., along line 4-5 by public land; on the SE., along lines 5-6-7 both by Forest Zone; and in the SW., and NW., along lines 7-8-1 both by Forest Zone.

Beginning at point marked “1” on plan being S. 00 deg. 03′ W., 8,759.15 meters from BLLM No. 1, Pls-533, thence:

134.31 m. to point 2;

288.95 m. to point 3;

25.00 m. to point 4;

119.88 m. to point 5;

203.50 m. to point 6;

553.20 m. to point 7;

350.09 m. to point 8;

636.40 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of Two Hundred Thirty Four Thousand Eight Hundred Eleven (234,811) square meters , more or less.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PS cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 40 cms. Bearings True; Date of Original Survey: Not Indicated; Date of Perimeter Survey May 9-11, 2000 executed by Geodetic Engineer Leonardo B. Tagal, Jr. and approved on June 14, 2001.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 24th day of May in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

